data.description:
This beautifully designed 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home by Woodside masterfully combines modern elegance with functional design. It showcases a split floor plan with each bedroom being spacious and private. The entryway, adorned with custom carpentry and exquisite wainscotting, opens to a living space with wood-like laminate flooring and walls in designer colors. The kitchen, a chef's delight, features granite countertops, under-cabinet lighting, stainless steel appliances, and a central island. The owner's suite is a spacious
sanctuary with an en-suite bathroom that includes a standing shower and soaking tub. Outdoors, the large backyard with a gorgeous covered patio and extended cement area offers versatile space, including the potential for RV parking. You'll love the OWNED solar panels, significantly cutting energy costs.
Additionally, for veterans, there's a VA Loan assumption option at an attractive 2.5% interest rate. Located close to NAS Lemoore and with easy access to the 198 freeway, this home's location is unbeatably convenient. Don't miss this opportunity for a perfect blend of comfort, style, and practicality. Schedule your showing today!
